---
description: E2E test naming convention (b2c/b2b + guest/registered + action)
alwaysApply: true
globs:
  - "**/*.ts"
  - "**/*.tsx"
  - "**/*.js"
  - "**/*.jsx"
  - "**/*.mjs"
  - "**/*.cjs"
---

For new or renamed specs under `e2e/playwright/tests/**`, use this filename convention:

- `b2c-guest-<action>.spec.ts`
- `b2c-registered-<action>.spec.ts`
- `b2b-guest-<action>.spec.ts`
- `b2b-registered-<action>.spec.ts`

Where `<action>` is a short, hyphenated description, for example:

- `checkout-place-order-braintree-paypal`
- `checkout-place-order-braintree-card`
- `pdp-add-to-cart`

Keep names stable and descriptive; avoid embedding store codes (siteId) in filenames.
